Package: linux-clipboard-history
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Linux Clipboard History contributors
Depends: libgtk-4-1, xclip, xdotool, wl-clipboard
Description: Persistent clipboard history manager for Linux
 A GTK4 clipboard history application inspired by the Windows 11 clipboard
 manager. It supports searchable plain-text history, pinned items, X11 global
 shortcuts and auto-paste, and safe Wayland clipboard restoration.
